Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船内居然有Vajra的幼虫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.22,0:00:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不可能!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没想到你在策划政变啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这下该结束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.33,0:00:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惜 你们迟了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.35,0:00:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特 我想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.01,0:00:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心情 一定要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.15,0:00:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道这到底是好还是坏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是好事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都会想向自己喜欢的人表白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.10,0:00:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个美妙的舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.78,0:00:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还想唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.27,0:01:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过了吧 我已经不想再唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.11,0:01:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露·诺姆已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别骗人了 雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.87,0:01:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不会放弃唱歌的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.57,0:01:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌怎么能传达给那么多人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.92,0:01:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也算登过台演过戏的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看出什么是真的　什么是假装的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.39,0:01:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.28,0:01:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又怎么样呢　米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.63,0:01:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的喜欢的人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.06,0:03:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.32,0:03:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊…我没法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.32,0:04:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二形态的Vajra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.32,0:04:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.16,0:04:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快开车
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说「已经晚了」?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜 我们的婚约只能作废了 凯茜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.30,0:05:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.05,0:05:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是任务完成得报告吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.81,0:05:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我　三岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻回你那里去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你留在那里别动
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.11,0:05:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.37,0:05:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊　三岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Vajra吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.01,0:05:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.72,0:05:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌能让那些家伙老实下来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.16,0:05:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了保护这个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了大家 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.62,0:06:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 我还是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.68,0:06:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 我唱不了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.75,0:06:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况没法唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经很讨厌这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是跟Vajra战斗的道具
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:53.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道唱歌需要心情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.77,0:07:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是职业歌手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做自己能做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:06.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声里有特别的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有无论我怎样祈求都无法得到的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.93,0:07:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:07:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 七濑 现在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心好疼 好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.65,0:08:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然变得更加激烈了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感情水平 -7.3
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这到底是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.33,0:09:10.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.62,0:09:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像是11年前的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.10,0:09:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你搞的鬼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.21,0:09:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.57,0:09:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我估计过这种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说也是突发性事件了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个你那样也好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总统好像还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什么困难 要我来帮忙你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会自己做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个骚乱是上天安排的好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.88,0:09:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Island内出现了Vajra?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.63,0:09:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令部有了紧急返回的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.78,0:09:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是已经摆脱Vajra了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.24,0:09:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Defold 反应
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.33,0:09:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Vajra
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.23,0:10:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么会有这么多Vajra呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是在岛内繁殖了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个尺度的 还好抢对他们有效
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这么多数量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.57,0:10:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之先去SMS基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.42,0:10:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了那里 也能补充武器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.42,0:10:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是暂时状态不太好而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.21,0:10:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华的歌是大家的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.82,0:10:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是声音强度不足
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.04,0:10:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去SMS基地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.22,0:10:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里有卡娜丽亚的机体留下来的Fold波增幅器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那个一定能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.52,0:10:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七濑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等 我马上就
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.82,0:11:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.86,0:11:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快去停止这个骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.41,0:11:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.95,0:11:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.97,0:11:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会来救你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:27.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华 发什么呆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特的手好热
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.89,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 以前也被人牵着过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的手也是很热
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.57,0:11:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部的Vajra引来援军了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.76,0:11:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们接近船队
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.40,0:12:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋月号 被击沉!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.20,0:12:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了 Vajra向船队靠近!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.17,0:12:38.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天蝎1号 敌人也会从外面攻过来 交由你来对付
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Frontier现在被毁灭的话我也会困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.04,0:12:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vajra绝对不会伤害Little Queen
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.43,0:12:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想进入强制模式的话就乖乖听从命令
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连接
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和兰华取得联络没有?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.55,0:13:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竭尽全力把她找出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.15,0:13:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平安无事吗 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.05,0:13:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府职能已经全部转移至Battle Frontier上了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:53.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后就在那里做指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深表感谢 阁下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.61,0:14:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后的事就交付给我 莱昂·三岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈尼 为什么 为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.38,0:14:13.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.08,0:14:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗还有阵亡 这些交给军队承担不就够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静下来 你这笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是这时候需要冷静 听到了吗 米歇尔?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克兰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢卡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有能使用的武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.12,0:14:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据数据显示 大约有些EX-gear以及Valkyrie用的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:41.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 就靠这些可对付不了那些家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 这正好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.04,0:14:45.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克兰 你!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.76,0:14:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到Battle Frontier里有这近路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.78,0:14:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里只有政府要员 总统以及其家属知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.40,0:15:01.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.66,0:15:03.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.79,0:15:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特 再打倒两三只后就一口气跑过去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.32,0:15:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.84,0:15:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克兰 准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.71,0:15:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔 刚才的答案能告诉我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.42,0:15:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢的人在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.16,0:15:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下落不明 现在搜索中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.21,0:15:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的东西有还是没有 说不定我自己都忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.64,0:16:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 的确 你是个胆小鬼!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.13,0:16:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你 米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 在这节骨眼上都说些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 就因为在这节骨眼上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了 米歇尔 给我好好记住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特 你这家伙也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.43,0:16:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕死的话…怎么谈得了恋爱!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.07,0:16:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.87,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.87,0:16:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿露特 掩护克兰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.07,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:46.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓紧了 兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.91,0:16:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李兰华怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.92,0:17:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子唱歌的话 Vajra不就会停止进攻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明说能够逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就觉得政府那些家伙的说法太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.69,0:17:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了 我们要死了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们 会死吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.52,0:17:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 爱迪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.05,0:17:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈她们一定 一定会保护我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.43,0:17:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我好怕 爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别哭 就算有万一 爸爸也会以生命保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以生命…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不可能放弃唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是那样的话 你的歌声又怎么能够传达给那么多人听?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.58,0:18:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歌吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信还能够传达给别人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰华
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.40,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你是希望的歌姬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就在绝望中歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有救援吗 军队呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来人啊 做点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.82,0:18:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:18:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雪露
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,银河的妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.74,0:19:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好美啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.30,0:19:48.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱迪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fold波增幅器没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.84,0:20:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了 朝你那边过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.93,0:20:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.97,0:20:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说阿露特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真心喜欢一个人的话 即使拼上性命也在所不惜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你们得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:20:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.24,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.94,0:21:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.72,0:21:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个臭虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克兰…克兰…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.52,0:21:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都没有说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也…我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.39,0:21:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱着…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.93,0:22:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米歇尔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.69,0:23:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法消除的伤痕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.07,0:23:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺痛着每个人的心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.55,0:23:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将人们引向诀别之时
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一级　蓝色的宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.35,0:23:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲恋之歌　响于银河
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,---------------------------------in
